title: Design, synthesis, biological evaluation, and docking studies of novel triazolo[4,3-b]pyridazine derivatives as dual c-Met/Pim-1 potential inhibitors with antitumor activity
content:
RSC Adv., 2024, 14,30346-30363
DOI: 10.1039/D4RA04036H, Paper

Mohamed E. Mahmoud, Eman M. Ahmed, Hamdy M. Ragab, Rania Farag A. Eltelbany, Rasha A. Hassan
New series of triazolo[4,3-b]pyridazine derivatives were created. Compounds 4a and 4g demonstrated extensive antiproliferative activity on various cell lines. Compound 4g displayed higher dual inhibition on c-Met and Pim-1.
